003package es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.corenlplemmatization.entity;
004
005import javax.persistence.Entity;
006import javax.persistence.Table;
007
008import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.entity.ProcessedDocumentWithTitle;
009
010/**
011 * Represents a lemmatized text document which has a title.
012 *
013 * @author Alejandro González García
014 * @implNote The implementation of this class is not thread-safe.
015 */
016@Entity
017@Table(name = "lemmatized_text_with_title_document")
018public class CoreNLPLemmatizedTextWithTitleDocument extends ProcessedDocumentWithTitle {
019        /**
020         * Creates a new lemmatized text document which has a title with the given
021         * parameters.
022         *
023         * @param id    The ID of the lemmatized text document with title, that must
024         *              match the ID of a text document which has a title.
025         * @param text  The lemmatized text of the document.
026         * @param title The lemmatized title of the text document.
027         * @throws IllegalArgumentException If any argument is {@code null}.
028         */
029        public CoreNLPLemmatizedTextWithTitleDocument(final int id, final String text, final String title) {
030                super(id, text, title);
031        }
032
033        /**
034         * Dummy constructor that only assigns a primary key. Intended for usage when
035         * the rest of the entity attributes are to be be assigned later.
036         *
037         * @param id The primary key of the entity.
038         * @throws IllegalArgumentException If {@code id} is {@code null}.
039         */
040        public CoreNLPLemmatizedTextWithTitleDocument(final Integer id) {
041                super(id);
042        }
043
044        /**
045         * Dummy default constructor, to be used by JPA only.
046         */
047        protected CoreNLPLemmatizedTextWithTitleDocument() {}
048}
